## ğŸ“ Dataset

The dataset used contains Hinglish utterances and corresponding intents, structured like:

```csv
text,intent
"main youtube kholna chahta hoon",open_youtube
"camera open karo",open_camera
"time kya hua hai",get_time
...
```

> ğŸ“Œ **Note:** The dataset is either loaded from a local `CSV` file or embedded within the notebook itself.

